The paper discusses the use of AI in cybersecurity, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the current scope and application of AI in cybersecurity (cs.AI), as well as the use of learning techniques (cs.LG) and the adversarial nature of cybersecurity (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper touches on the implications for security operations centers (cs.SE).
